message.content:
1. The data set is complete with 195 entries.
2. The 95% confidence interval coverage is equivalent for ANCOVA and cLDA.
3. The estimated mean low-density lipoprotein (LDL) cholesterol is 11.2 mg/dL lower in GMC compared to usual care.
4. The 95% confidence interval for the difference in LDL cholesterol levels between GMC and usual care is -19.2 to -3.3.
5. The p-value for the difference in LDL cholesterol levels between GMC and usual care is 0.006.
